hai\n* [[Ramida Jiranorraphat]] (Jane) as Lin\n\n=== Supporting ===\n* [[Pongkool Suebsung]] as Thong\n* [[Jirakit Thawornwong]] (Mek) as Luke\n* [[Juthapich Inn-Chan]] (Jamie) as Punpun\n* [[Gornpop Janjaroen]] (Joke) as Stephen Shepherd (Police Angel)\n* [[Sumonrat Wattanaselarat]] as Rarin\n* [[Phatchara Tubthong]] (Kapook) as Dujao\n* [[Worranit Thawornwong]] (Mook) as Serena\n* [[Pattadon Janngeon]] (Fiat) as Gabriel (Angel)\n\n=== Guest role ===\n* [[Pronpiphat Pattanasettanon]] (Plustor) as Guardian Angel\n* [[Niti Chaichitathorn]] (Pompam) as Lord of Angels\n* [[Napasorn Weerayuttvilai]] (Puimek) as Angel of Love\n* [[Purim Rattanaruangwattana]] (Pluem) as Angel\n* [[Harit Cheewagaroon]] (Sing)\n* [[Chanagun Arpornsutinan]] (Gunsmile) as Munggorn\n* [[Rachanun Mahawan]] (Film) as Baitoey\n\n== Soundtrack ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Song Title\n!Artist\n!Ref\n|-\n| ''Beside You''\n| [[Apiwat Phongwat]]\n| <ref>{{cite web |title=Beside You Ost.\u0e40\u0e17\u0e27\u0e14\u0e32\u0e17\u0e48\u0e32\u0e08\u0e30\u0e23\u0e31\u0e01 Angel Beside Me - \u0e2b\u0e19\u0e36\u0e48\u0e07 \u0e2d\u0e20\u0e34\u0e27\u0e31\u0e12\u0e19\u0e4c |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6_fXeDRiFxQ |website=youtube.com |publisher=[[GMMTV]] Records |accessdate=15 April 2020}}</ref>\n|}\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* [https://www.gmm25.com/shows_detail.html?id=861 GMM 25 Show Details] {{in lang|th}}\n* [https://tv.line.me/angelbesideme \u0e40\u0e17\u0e27\u0e14\u0e32\u0e17\u0e48\u0e32\u0e08\u0e30\u0e23\u0e31\u0e01 Angel Beside Me - LINE TV]\n* [http://www.gmm-tv.com GMMTV]\n\n{{GMMTV television series|state=expanded}}\n[[Category:Television series by GMMTV]]\n[[Category:Thai romantic comedy television series]]\n[[Category:2020 Thai television series debuts]]\n[[Category:2020 Thai television series endings]]\n[[Category:GMM 25 television programmes]]\n[[Category:Thai romantic fantasy television series]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|2020 Thai romantic fantasy d