 1972|1972]]'''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''70.0%''' ''10,277''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Democratic}}|29.9% ''4,395''\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:honeyDew;\"|0.1% ''20''\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''[[United States presidential election in Illinois, 1968|1968]]'''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''60.5%''' ''8,638''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Democratic}}|31.9% ''4,552''\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:honeyDew;\"|7.7% ''1,099''\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Democratic}}|'''[[United States presidential election in Illinois, 1964|1964]]'''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|46.9% ''6,805''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Democratic}}|'''53.1%''' ''7,712''\n|\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''[[United States presidential election in Illinois, 1960|1960]]'''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''62.2%''' ''9,383''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Democratic}}|37.7% ''5,691''\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:honeyDew;\"|0.1% ''16''\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''[[United States presidential election in Illinois, 1956|1956]]'''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''66.6%''' ''9,589''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Democratic}}|33.3% ''4,793''\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:honeyDew;\"|0.1% ''14''\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''[[1952 United States presidential election|1952]]'''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|'''64.4%''' ''9,162''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Democratic}}|35.5% ''5,048''\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:honeyDew;\"|0.1% ''19''\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"